  m_text: 'Target : The transform followed by the camera.

    Offset : The offset
    appiled to the camera. Define where it should place itself relative to the target.

    FollowMode
    : The Update cycle in which the camera update it''s position. Changing it can
    induce or reduce jittering.

    Follow Damping : How stringly the camera follow
    the player when he is moving. 0 means the camera is always on the player'
