      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Has Look ahead : Wether the player will have the look ahead ability.

    Input
    : The input used to control the look ahead.

    Look ahead: The limiting value
    of the look ahead, it works both as a limit for the minimum value and the maximum
    value.

    Smoothing Time : The time it take for the look ahead to go from it''s
    default value to it''s maximum value.

    Easing Type : The easing that will
    be applied to the smoothing.'
