      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Has Collider : Wether the camera detect collision of object impairing
    it''s view of the target.

    Collision Radius : The radius of the camera. Help
    define at which position the calera needs to be placed if a collision has been
    detected.

    Coolision mask : The layers the camera can detect a collision
    in.

    Collision query :  How the camera should behave when the collider in
    front of it is a trigger.

    Smoothing Time : The time it take for the look
    ahead to go from it''s default value to it''s maximum value.

    Easing Type
    : The easing that will be applied to the smoothing.'
